8 Data Types in Java (Basic)
	Number
		int, Integer : 4 Bytes
		short, Short : 2 Bytes
		byte, Byte : 1 Byte
		long, Long : 8 Bytes
		float, Float : 4 Bytes
		double, Double : 8 Bytes
	Boolean
		boolean, Boolean : true/false
		
	Character
		char, Character
	String
		

